    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is a solid choice for someone looking for a reliable commuter that needs a bit of cosmetic attention. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some paint fading on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear, particularly on the driver's seat, and the air conditioning takes a few minutes to get cold. Mechanically, it runs well, though it will likely need new brake pads and a tune-up in the near future. It\u2019s a dependable car that just needs a little TLC to be great again.",
