    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable ride that gets the job done? This vehicle is in honest, fair condition and ready for its next adventure! While it shows some expected signs of use and minor cosmetic wear, it remains a dependable choice that drives well. It's a fantastic opportunity to own a solid, functional car at a price that offers incredible value!",
